refentry.refsect1:
&ref.title.attributes;


  Attributes for <path> tag

  &taskAttributes.table.titlesLine.all;



    dir

    String

    Specific path to directory

    &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

    &attributes.required.no;




    path

    String

    A path (which contains multiple locations separated by
    path.separator) to add.

    &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

    &attributes.required.no;

    &ref.title.supportedNestedTags;


The <path> tag supports nested
    <fileset> and <dirset> tags.
